                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?auto=format&fit=crop&w=200&q=80" alt="Customer" class="rounded-circle" style="width: 64px; height: 64px; object-fit: cover;" loading="lazy">
